{"heading":"The Jews despise the Lord by offering polluted bread upon the altar and by sacrificing animals with blemishes—The Lord’s name will be great among the Gentiles.","number":1,"verseCount":14,"verses":[[1,["The burden of the ",["word",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Priesthood, Keys of","tg/priesthood-keys-of"],"."]]]," of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," to Israel by Malachi."]],[2,["I have ",["loved",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Love of","tg/god-love-of"],"; ",["Love","tg/love"],"."]]]," you, saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],". Yet ye say, Wherein hast thou loved us? ",["Was",["clarity-word"]]," not Esau Jacob’s brother? saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],": yet I ",["loved",["study-note-ref","b",[["Rom. 9:13","nt/rom/9.13"],"."]]]," Jacob,"]],[3,["And I hated Esau, and laid his mountains and his ",["heritage",["study-note-ref","a",[["Jer. 49:10","ot/jer/49.10"],"."]]]," ",["waste",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ezek. 25:13","ot/ezek/25.13"],"."]]]," for the ",["dragons",["study-note-ref","c",["HEB jackals."]]]," of the wilderness."]],[4,["Whereas Edom saith, We are impoverished, but we will return and build the desolate places; thus saith the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," of hosts, They shall build, but I will throw down; and they shall call them, The border of wickedness, and, The people against whom the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," hath indignation for ever."]],[5,["And your eyes shall see, and ye shall say, The ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," will be magnified from the border of Israel."]],[6,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"A son ",["honoureth",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Family, Children, Duties of","tg/family-children-duties-of"],"."]]]," ",["his",["clarity-word"]]," father, and a servant his master: if then I ",["be",["clarity-word"]]," a father, where ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," mine ",["honour",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Honoring Father and Mother","tg/honoring-fat